Welcome to the Cave Defender Central Server! We hope your time here will be filled with laughter, fond memories and a whole bunch of distruction or defense (whichever you prefer.)
There are a few things that we would like you to keep in mind while playing here. They are as follows.

1. Before you can play, you must read and agree to follow this servers rules. Reasons such as, "I didn't know what the rules stated" or similar will not be tolerated when deciding on punishments to be handed out for rule breakage, should such become necessary.
2. Attempting to negate or otherwise lessen any punishment(s) handed out for rule breakage will result in said punishment(s) being increased and, if necessary, temporary or permanant bans may be issued if the need arises.
3. Attempting to shift blame for your actions onto another person, including but not limited to staff, may result in punishment(s) either being delt or increased.

Thank you, and once again, we hope you enjoy your time here!
